This is a '''list of hemophilia organizations''', it includes the numerous organizations around the world which are formed for the support of people with [[hemophilia]], including advocacy and education groups.<ref>[http://www.wfh.org/2/8/8_5_Link1_Nat%27lHemoSites.htm List of National Hemophilia Sites] World Federation of Hemophilia</ref> Hemophilia (or Haemophilia) is a group of [[heredity|hereditary]] [[genetic disorder]]s that impair the body's ability to control [[blood]] clotting or [[coagulation]], which is used to stop bleeding when a [[blood vessel]] is broken.

